### User Experience Risks
- **Search Frustration**: Clear progress indicators and time estimates
- **Information Overload**: Smart filtering and sorting options
- **Trust Issues**: Transparent source attribution and confidence scores
- **Learning Curve**: Intuitive UI with contextual help

